             was indicted for the <rs id="t18140914-44-off249" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18140914-44-off249" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140914-44-off249" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               wilful murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18140914-44-victim422" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Davis
                        <interp inst="t18140914-44-victim422" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18140914-44-victim422" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18140914-44-victim422" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
